---
const appUrl = 'https://verbs.jcvb.com.co';
const games = [
  { name: 'Quick Match', desc: 'Selección múltiple con vidas y rachas', icon: '⚡', color: '#667eea' },
  { name: 'Speed Challenge', desc: 'Une pares en 60 segundos', icon: '⏱️', color: '#f093fb' },
  { name: 'Type Master', desc: 'Escribe la respuesta exacta', icon: '⌨️', color: '#4f46e5' },
  { name: 'Memory Cards', desc: 'Voltea y empareja tarjetas', icon: '🃏', color: '#06b6d4' },
  { name: 'Practice', desc: 'Navega y pon a prueba tu memoria', icon: '📖', color: '#10b981' },
];
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
  <title>alunas — Aprende cualquier tema jugando</title>
  <meta name="description" content="alunas convierte tu material de estudio en juegos interactivos para memorizar cualquier tema de forma efectiva y divertida." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="alunas — Aprende cualquier tema jugando" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Convierte tu material de estudio en juegos interactivos." />
  <meta property="og:image" content="/og.png" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0f24" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/logo.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo" aria-label="alunas home">
    <img src="/logo.svg" alt="alunas logo" height="32" />
  </a>
  <a href={appUrl} class="btn btn-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir app →</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="badge">Disponible ahora · Gratis · Sin registro</div>
    <h1>Aprende <em>cualquier tema</em><br/>jugando</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      alunas transforma tu material de estudio en juegos interactivos.<br/>
      Practica con 5 modos de juego, compite con otros y memoriza más rápido.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href={appUrl} class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en el navegador</a>
      <a href="#instalar" class="btn btn-ghost">Instalar en mi celular ↓</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-preview">
      <div class="phone-mockup">
        <div class="phone-screen">
          <div class="screen-top">
            <img src="/logo.svg" alt="alunas" height="28" />
            <span class="screen-badge">5 juegos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="game-cards-preview">
            {games.map(g => (
              <div class="game-pill" style={`background: ${g.color}22; border-color: ${g.color}44`}>
                <span>{g.icon}</span>
                <span>{g.name}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="how">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Cómo funciona</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">📚</div>
        <h3>Elige un tema</h3>
        <p>Selecciona el contenido que quieres aprender. Actualmente: verbos y sustantivos irregulares en inglés.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">🎮</div>
        <h3>Elige un juego</h3>
        <p>5 modos de juego distintos para diferentes estilos de aprendizaje. Desde selección múltiple hasta escritura libre.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">🏆</div>
        <h3>Practica y compite</h3>
        <p>Supera tus récords, crea Universos para practicar en grupo y ve tu progreso en tiempo real.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- GAMES -->
<section class="games">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>5 modos de juego</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Cada modo usa una mecánica diferente para reforzar la memoria</p>
    <div class="games-grid">
      {games.map(g => (
        <div class="game-card" style={`--c: ${g.color}`}>
          <div class="game-icon">{g.icon}</div>
          <h3>{g.name}</h3>
          <p>{g.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- UNIVERSES -->
<section class="universes">
  <div class="container universes-inner">
    <div class="universes-text">
      <h2>Aprende en grupo con Universos</h2>
      <p>Crea o únete a un Universo — un espacio compartido donde todos practican el mismo tema y compiten en un marcador en tiempo real. Perfecto para salones de clase o grupos de estudio.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>✓ Crea tu Universo con un código único</li>
        <li>✓ Comparte el enlace o código QR</li>
        <li>✓ Marcador en vivo con todos los puntajes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="universes-visual">
      <div class="leaderboard-mockup">
        <div class="lb-title">🏆 Universo: Inglés B2</div>
        <div class="lb-row lb-first"><span>1. Sofía</span><span class="lb-score">2,840</span></div>
        <div class="lb-row lb-second"><span>2. Mateo</span><span class="lb-score">2,510</span></div>
        <div class="lb-row lb-third"><span>3. Valentina</span><span class="lb-score">2,230</span></div>
        <div class="lb-row"><span>4. Tú</span><span class="lb-score">1,980</span></div>
        <div class="lb-row"><span>5. Carlos</span><span class="lb-score">1,740</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INSTALAR PWA -->
<section class="install" id="instalar">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Instálala en tu dispositivo</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">alunas es una PWA — funciona como app nativa sin pasar por la App Store ni Play Store</p>

    <div class="install-grid">

      <!-- iOS -->
      <div class="install-card">
        <div class="install-os">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.8-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/></svg>
          iPhone / iPad
        </div>
        <ol>
          <li>Abre <strong>Safari</strong> y ve a <code>verbs.jcvb.com.co</code></li>
          <li>Toca el botón de <strong>Compartir</strong> <span class="icon-inline">⎙</span></li>
          <li>Desplázate y toca <strong>"Agregar a pantalla de inicio"</strong></li>
          <li>Toca <strong>Agregar</strong> — ya aparece el ícono en tu pantalla</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="install-note">Funciona offline y a pantalla completa</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Android -->
      <div class="install-card">
        <div class="install-os">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.6 9.48l1.84-3.18c.16-.31.04-.69-.26-.85-.29-.15-.65-.06-.83.22l-1.88 3.24c-2.86-1.21-6.08-1.21-8.94 0L5.65 5.67c-.19-.29-.58-.38-.87-.2-.28.18-.37.54-.22.83L6.4 9.48C3.3 11.25 1.28 14.44 1 18h22c-.28-3.56-2.3-6.75-5.4-8.52zM7 15.25c-.69 0-1.25-.56-1.25-1.25S6.31 12.75 7 12.75s1.25.56 1.25 1.25-.56 1.25-1.25 1.25zm10 0c-.69 0-1.25-.56-1.25-1.25s.56-1.25 1.25-1.25 1.25.56 1.25 1.25-.56 1.25-1.25 1.25z"/></svg>
          Android
        </div>
        <ol>
          <li>Abre <strong>Chrome</strong> y ve a <code>verbs.jcvb.com.co</code></li>
          <li>Toca el menú <strong>⋮</strong> (tres puntos arriba a la derecha)</li>
          <li>Toca <strong>"Agregar a pantalla de inicio"</strong> o <strong>"Instalar app"</strong></li>
          <li>Confirma — el ícono aparece en tu pantalla principal</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="install-note">También puedes tocar el banner de instalación que aparece automáticamente</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Desktop -->
      <div class="install-card">
        <div class="install-os">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20 18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2H0v2h24v-2h-4zM4 6h16v10H4V6z"/></svg>
          Desktop (Chrome / Edge)
        </div>
        <ol>
          <li>Abre <strong>Chrome o Edge</strong> y ve a <code>verbs.jcvb.com.co</code></li>
          <li>Haz clic en el ícono <strong>⊕</strong> en la barra de direcciones</li>
          <li>Haz clic en <strong>"Instalar"</strong></li>
          <li>La app se abre en su propia ventana como app nativa</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="install-note">Aparece en tu lista de apps instaladas del sistema</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="install-cta">
      <a href={appUrl} class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir alunas →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <a href="/" class="footer-logo">
      <img src="/logo.svg" alt="alunas" height="28" />
    </a>
    <p class="footer-copy">alunas · Aprende la forma divertida</p>
    <a href={appUrl} class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">verbs.jcvb.com.co</a>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --cyan: #00f0ff;
    --green: #00ffa3;
    --dark: #0a0f24;
    --dark2: #0f1730;
    --dark3: #1a2545;
    --text: #e2e8f0;
    --muted: #8892aa;
    --r: 12px;
    --t: 0.18s ease;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10,15,36,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.08);
  }
  .nav-logo img { display: block; }

  /* BUTTONS */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform var(--t), box-shadow var(--t), background var(--t);
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
  }
  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .btn-sm { padding: 0.45rem 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .btn-lg { padding: 0.9rem 2rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--green));
    color: var(--dark);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,240,255,0.25);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(0,240,255,0.4); }
  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--cyan);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.3);
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(0,240,255,0.06); border-color: var(--cyan); }
  nav .btn { background: rgba(0,240,255,0.1); color: var(--cyan); border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.2); }
  nav .btn:hover { background: rgba(0,240,255,0.15); }

  /* CONTAINER */
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 92vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 700px;
    height: 700px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,240,255,0.07) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(0,255,163,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,163,0.25);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #fff;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--green));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }

  /* PHONE MOCKUP */
  .hero-preview { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .phone-mockup {
    width: 280px;
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(0,240,255,0.08), 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .phone-screen { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .screen-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .screen-badge {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: rgba(0,240,255,0.12);
    color: var(--cyan);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.2);
  }
  .game-cards-preview { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .game-pill {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  .how {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--dark2);
  }
  .how h2, .games h2, .universes h2, .install h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .step {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 220px;
    max-width: 280px;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .step-icon {
    width: 64px; height: 64px;
    background: var(--dark3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }
  .step h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
  .step p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .step-arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    opacity: 0.4;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* GAMES */
  .games { padding: 6rem 1.5rem; }
  .section-sub {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: -2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .games-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .game-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.2rem;
    transition: transform var(--t), border-color var(--t), box-shadow var(--t);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .game-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--c);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .game-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .game-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .game-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .game-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); }

  /* UNIVERSES */
  .universes { padding: 6rem 1.5rem; background: var(--dark2); }
  .universes-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .universes-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 280px;
  }
  .universes-text h2 { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .universes-text p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .universes-text ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .universes-text li { color: var(--text); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .universes-visual { flex: 1; min-width: 260px; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
  .leaderboard-mockup {
    background: var(--dark3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.12);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 320px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,240,255,0.05);
  }
  .lb-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: #fff; }
  .lb-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .lb-first { background: rgba(255,215,0,0.12); color: #ffd700; font-weight: 700; }
  .lb-second { background: rgba(192,192,192,0.1); color: #c0c0c0; font-weight: 600; }
  .lb-third { background: rgba(205,127,50,0.1); color: #cd7f32; font-weight: 600; }
  .lb-score { font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }

  /* INSTALL */
  .install { padding: 6rem 1.5rem; }
  .install-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .install-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color var(--t);
  }
  .install-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,240,255,0.2); }
  .install-os {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .install-card ol {
    padding-left: 1.4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .install-card li { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.5; }
  .install-card strong { color: #fff; }
  .install-card code {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    background: rgba(0,240,255,0.1);
    color: var(--cyan);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .icon-inline {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 22px; height: 22px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .install-note {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted);
